text: Hackås IF is a sports club in Hackås in Sweden. It was established in 1935. The women's bandy team has played two seasons in the Swedish top division. The women's soccer team played four seasons in the Swedish top division between 1978 and 1981. ==References== ==Other websites== *Official website Category:1935 establishments in Sweden Category:Swedish football clubs Category:Bandy clubs in Sweden
